### Inventory Database API Tests (Port 4000)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Create a New Supplier
POST {{baseUrl}}/supplier
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Global Electronics",
  "contact": "sales@globalelectronics.com"
}

###

### 3. List All Suppliers
GET {{baseUrl}}/suppliers
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Add an Inventory Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "High-Speed Processor",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "price": 299.99,
  "stock": 50,
  "supplierName": "Global Electronics"
}

###

### 5. List All Inventory Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Get Inventory Grouped by Supplier
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/grouped
Accept: application/json
